\c 34
\s Ukufa kukaMozisi
\p
\v 1 UMozisi wasesenyuka esuka emagcekeni akoMowabi, esiya entabeni yeNebo, engqongeni yePisiga, emaqondana leJeriko\x + Nani 27.12.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimtshengisa ilizwe lonke, iGileyadi kuze kube koDani\x + Hlu. 18.29.\x*,
\v 2 layo yonke iNafithali, lelizwe lakoEfrayimi, leManase, lelizwe lonke lakoJuda, kwaze kwaba selwandle lokucina\x + 11.24.\x*,
\v 3 leningizimu, legceke lesigodi seJeriko\x + Gen. 13.12. 19.17. 2 Sam. 18.23.\x*, umuzi wamalala\x + Hlu. 1.16. 3.13. 2 Lan. 28.15.\x*, kwaze kwaba seZowari\x + Gen. 14.2,8. 19.22.\x*.
\v 4 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Leli yilizwe engalifungela uAbrahama, uIsaka, loJakobe ngisithi: Ngizalinika inzalo yakho\x + Gen. 12.7. 50.24.\x*. Sengikwenze walibona ngamehlo akho, kodwa kawuyikuchaphela kilo\x + 3.27. 32.52.\x*.
\p
\v 5 UMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* wasefela khona elizweni lakoMowabi njengokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 6 Yasimngcwaba esigodini elizweni lakoMowabi maqondana leBeti-Peyori\x + Nani 23.28.\x*; kodwa kakulamuntu olaziyo ingcwaba lakhe kuze kube lamuhla\x + Juda 9.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Njalo uMozisi wayeleminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amabili ekufeni kwakhe\x + 31.2.\x*. Amehlo akhe ayengafiphalanga, lamandla akhe ayenganyamalalanga\x + Gen. 27.1. 1 Sam. 3.2. Gen. 48.10. Josh. 14.10,11. 1 Sam. 4.15.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebemlilela uMozisi emagcekeni akoMowabi insuku ezingamatshumi amathathu; zaphela-ke insuku zokukhala zokumlilela uMozisi\x + Nani 20.29. Gen. 50.3.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Njalo uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni wayegcwele umoya wokuhlakanipha\x + Isa. 11.2.\x*, ngoba uMozisi wayebekile izandla zakhe phezu kwakhe. Ngakho abantwana bakoIsrayeli bamlalela, benza njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* imlayile uMozisi\x + Nani 27.18,23.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Kakusavelanga-ke umprofethi koIsrayeli onjengoMozisi\x + 18.15,18.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyamazi ubuso ngobuso\x + Eks. 33.11. Hlu. 6.22. Nani 12.8. Dute. 5.4.\x*,
\v 11 ngazo zonke izibonakaliso lezimangaliso iN\nd kosi\nd* eyamthuma ukuthi azenze elizweni leGibhithe, kuFaro lakuzo zonke inceku zakhe lelizweni lakhe\x + 4.34. 7.19.\x* lonke,
\v 12 langaso sonke lesosandla esilamandla\x + 4.34.\x* langakho konke okwesabekayo okukhulu\x + 4.34.\x* uMozisi akwenzayo phambi kwamehlo kaIsrayeli wonke.
